  "texts": [
    "These steps provided the selection of the 12 variables that jointly perform well in the classification.",
    "Several machine-learning methods are available to solve classification problems.",
    "The two most commonly used are boost (Adaboost 44, XGboost 45) and bagging (Random Forests 46).",
    "For some problems, the performance of the two methods is very similar 47, 48.",
    "Combining a large number of trees improves prediction accuracy 41, therefore, ensemble methods are popular."
  ]
}